  "history": {
    "en": "The Japanese Bobtail is an active, sweet, loving and highly intelligent breed. They love to be with people and play seemingly endlessly. They learn their name and respond to it. They bring toys to people and play fetch with a favorite toy for hours. Bobtails are social and are at their best when in the company of people. They take over the house and are not intimidated. If a dog is in the house, Bobtails assume Bobtails are in charge.",
    "zh": "日本短尾猫是一种活跃、甜美、充满爱心且非常聪明的品种。它们喜欢与人在一起，似乎永无止境地玩耍。它们能学会自己的名字并做出回应。它们会带玩具给人，并花几个小时玩最喜欢的玩具的取回游戏。短尾猫善于社交，在与人相处时表现最佳。它们会占据整个家，并且不畏惧。如果家里有狗，短尾猫会认为它们说了算。"
  },
